description: What is a Kathi Roll? A healthy, hand-rolled whole wheat Indian-style tortilla, with an egg fried on top. Stuffed with spiced, grilled chicken or paneer, mint chutney, and pickled onions. Made from scratch with all-natural ingredients and no preservatives, these rolls are sure to hit the spot for your lunch. Find the Roll OK Please truck in the Seattle area and check it out!
name: Roll OK Please
